TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
Pre SQL
Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT distinct case when txt_remarks is not null and TXT_PAYMENT_CURRENCY = 'SGD' and TXT_SETTLMENT_WAY IN ('GIRO','LBC') and TXT_BUSINESS_UNIT = 'SGPPD' then 'MEPS' else OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_SETTLMENT_WAY end as TXT_SETTLMENT_WAY, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.DTE_CYCLE_DATE as DTE_CYCLE_DATE, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_CYCLE_TYPE as TXT_CYCLE_TYPE, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_BUSINESS_UNIT as TXT_BUSINESS_UNIT, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_PAYMENT_CURRENCY as TXT_PAYMENT_CURRENCY, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_EARNING_GROUP as TXT_EARNING_GROUP, OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_POSITION_NAME as TXT_POSITION_NAME FROM OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL WHERE OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_STATUS='ACTIVE' and NVL(OUT_PAYMENT_DETAIL.TXT_PAYMENT_METHOD,'-1') <>'C'

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: DTE_CYCLE_DATE = in_DTE_CYCLE_DATE AND TXT_CYCLE_TYPE = in_TXT_CYCLE_TYPE AND TXT_BUSINESS_UNIT = in_TXT_BUSINESS_UNIT AND TXT_PAYMENT_CURRENCY = in_TXT_PAYMENT_CURRENCY AND TXT_EARNING_GROUP = in_TXT_EARNING_GROUP AND TXT_POSITION_NAME = in_TXT_POSITION_NAME

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF( (:UDF.NVL_STR(TXT_BUSINESS_UNIT)='' and V_FA_FLAG='NOTFA'), ABORT('Agency/Agent code:' ||in_Agent_Name||'; Business unit is null ; '), IIF(V_FA_FLAG='FA', 'SGPAFA', IIF(V_FA_FLAG='NOTFA' and (TXT_BUSINESS_UNIT='SGPAFA' or (TXT_BUSINESS_UNIT='SGPIWH' and BUSINESSUNITMAP=128)), 'SGPAGY', :UDF.NVL_STR(TXT_BUSINESS_UNIT)) ) )
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: O_TXT_BUSINESS_UNIT

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
IIF( ( TXT_ACCT_CODE='BANKACCT' OR TXT_ACCT_CODE='CHECKACCT' ) AND ISNULL(V_SETTLMENT_WAY),
--add for FA agent, buisness unit is null to handle AIAS accounting, backacct, check acct may not have for negative payment iif ( V_FA_FLAG='NOTFA' AND TXT_BUSINESS_UNIT='SGPAFA' , 'GIRO', ABORT(iif(isnull (TXT_AGENT_POSITION_NAME), TXT_AGENCY_POSITION_NAME, TXT_AGENT_POSITION_NAME)||'Payment Settlment Way is null ; ') ), V_SETTLMENT_WAY)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: O_SETTLMENT_WAY

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF((TXT_ACCT_CODE='BANKACCT' OR TXT_ACCT_CODE='CHECKACCT') and V_FA_FLAG='NOTFA' , IIF((TXT_BUSINESS_UNIT='SGPAFA'), :LKP.LKP_CATEGORY('FA FIX ACCOUNT','AIAS_BANK_ACCT'), --change for gazelle project, for introducer unpaid special accounting code, will use another one IIF(TXT_BUSINESS_UNIT!='SGPIWH' AND ISNULL(:LKP.LKP_CATEGORY('GL ACCOUNT FOR BANK', V_SETTLMENT_WAY||'_'||IIF(ISNULL(TXT_AGENT_POSITION_NAME),TXT_AGENCY_POSITION_NAME,TXT_AGENT_POSITION_NAME)||'_'||TXT_ACCT_CURRENCY)), --end change :LKP.LKP_CATEGORY('GL ACCOUNT FOR BANK',V_SETTLMENT_WAY||'_'||TXT_ACCT_CURRENCY) --change for gazelle project, for introducer unpaid special accounting code, will use another one , IIF(TXT_BUSINESS_UNIT='SGPIWH',:LKP.LKP_CATEGORY('IWHBANK',V_SETTLMENT_WAY||'_'||TXT_ACCT_CURRENCY),:LKP.LKP_CATEGORY('GL ACCOUNT FOR BANK', V_SETTLMENT_WAY||'_'||IIF(ISNULL(TXT_AGENT_POSITION_NAME),TXT_AGENCY_POSITION_NAME,TXT_AGENT_POSITION_NAME)||'_'||TXT_ACCT_CURRENCY) ) --end change )), IIF((TXT_ACCT_CODE='BANKACCT' OR TXT_ACCT_CODE='CHECKACCT') and V_FA_FLAG='FA' , :LKP.LKP_CATEGORY('FABANK',V_SETTLMENT_WAY||'_'||TXT_ACCT_CURRENCY), TXT_ACCT_CODE) )
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: V_ACC_CODE

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF((TXT_ACCT_CODE='BANKACCT' OR TXT_ACCT_CODE='CHECKACCT' ) AND ISNULL(V_ACC_CODE),ABORT('Acc Code is null ; settlment way is '||V_SETTLMENT_WAY||' ; and currency code is '||TXT_ACCT_CURRENCY),V_ACC_CODE)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: O_ACC_CODE

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Join Condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: TXT_ACCT_CURRENCY = txtCurrency AND O_GA1_AGY_STATUS = O_txtAgt_Status AND TXT_AGENT_POSITION_NAME = O_txtAgt_no

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT case when CS_BUSINESSUNIT.name is null then 'SGP_Multi_Channel' else CS_BUSINESSUNIT.NAME end as BU_NAME, CS_POSITION.NAME AS POS_NAME, CS_POSITION.GENERICATTRIBUTE10 AS GA10 FROM CS_POSITION INNER join cs_payee on CS_POSITION.REMOVEDATE= to_date('01/01/2200 00:00:00', 'MM/DD/YYYY HH24:MI:SS') and CS_POSITION.islast =1 and cs_payee.removedate =to_date('01/01/2200 00:00:00', 'MM/DD/YYYY HH24:MI:SS') and cs_payee.islast =1 and CS_POSITION.payeeseq = cs_payee.payeeseq left join CS_BUSINESSUNIT ON CS_BUSINESSUNIT.MASK = cs_payee.BUSINESSUNITMAP AND CS_BUSINESSUNIT.PROCESSINGUNITSEQ =CS_POSITION.PROCESSINGUNITSEQ

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT A.GENERICATTRIBUTE1 AS GA1_AGY_STATUS, O.NAME AS AGY_NAME FROM CS_POSITION O, CS_PARTICIPANT A, IN_ETL_CONTROL C WHERE C.TXT_KEY_STRING = 'OPER_CYCLE_DATE' AND C.TXT_FILE_NAME = 'GLOBAL' AND O.PAYEESEQ = A.PAYEESEQ -- AND O.NAME = 'SGT30100' AND O.REMOVEDATE = TO_DATE('2200-01-01', 'YYYY-MM-DD') AND A.REMOVEDATE = TO_DATE('2200-01-01', 'YYYY-MM-DD') AND O.EFFECTIVESTARTDATE <= TO_DATE(C.TXT_KEY_VALUE, 'YYYY-MM-DD') AND O.EFFECTIVEENDDATE > TO_DATE(C.TXT_KEY_VALUE, 'YYYY-MM-DD') AND A.EFFECTIVESTARTDATE <= TO_DATE(C.TXT_KEY_VALUE, 'YYYY-MM-DD') AND A.EFFECTIVEENDDATE > TO_DATE(C.TXT_KEY_VALUE, 'YYYY-MM-DD')

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
IIF((NOT ISNULL(O_GA1_AGY_STATUS)) AND O_GA1_AGY_STATUS='70',
IIF(ISNULL(O_txtAgt_no) ,TXT_ACCT_AMOUNT,ROUND(TXT_ACCT_AMOUNT * dec_benef_perc / 100,2)) ,TXT_ACCT_AMOUNT)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: O_ACCT_AMOUNT

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(O_GA1_AGY_STATUS='70' AND (NOT ISNULL(O_txtPaymentMethod)), --bug fix, if it's benificaiary and it's FA agent, then still go to GIRO. iif ( O_FA_FLAG='NOTFA' AND TXT_BUSINESS_UNIT='SGPAFA' , 'GIRO',O_txtPaymentMethod) --end ,TXT_SETTLMENT_WAY)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: O_SETTLMENT_WAY

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION:
IIF((NOT ISNULL(O_GA1_AGY_STATUS)) AND O_GA1_AGY_STATUS='70', IIF( ( not ISNULL(O_txtAgt_no)) and ( not isnull(O_txtPaymentMethod)) , --bug fix, if it's benificaiary and it's FA agent, then still go to GIRO. iif ( O_FA_FLAG='NOTFA' AND TXT_BUSINESS_UNIT='SGPAFA' , :LKP.LKP_CATEGORY('GL ACCOUNT FOR BANK','GIRO'||'_'||TXT_ACCT_CURRENCY), :LKP.LKP_CATEGORY('GL ACCOUNT FOR BANK',O_txtPaymentMethod||'_'||TXT_ACCT_CURRENCY)), --:LKP.LKP_CATEGORY('GL ACCOUNT FOR BANK',O_txtPaymentMethod||'_'||TXT_ACCT_CURRENCY), TXT_ACC_CODE)
,TXT_ACC_CODE)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: O_ACC_CODE

TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: select t.*,row_number() over(partition by s_decea_agent order by dec_benef_perc,s_benef_nric,rowid) as rn from IN_AGENT_DECEASED_BENEF t
